@startuml
title Alarm Clock - State Machine Diagram

[*] --> Off

state "Off" as Off
state "Alarm Set" as AlarmSet
state "Ringing" as Ringing
state "Stopped" as Stopped

Off : do / Initialize System

Off --> AlarmSet : User Sets Alarm Time
AlarmSet --> Ringing : Current Time Matches Alarm Time
AlarmSet --> Off : User Turns Off Alarm

Ringing : do / Ring Alarm

Ringing --> Stopped : User Stops Alarm
Stopped --> AlarmSet : Next Scheduled Alarm Time

@enduml
